# Netlify _redirects
# Docs: https://docs.netlify.com/routing/redirects/

# ── Admin secret URL guard ──
# /admin alone with no code → redirect home (blocked)
/admin          /       302

# /admin/CODE → rewrite to admin panel (JS will verify the code)
/admin/*        /admin/index.html   200

# ── Customer page routes ──
# Root is handled by /index.html (splash page)
# /customer/* is served directly as static files (no rewrite needed)

# ── Catch-all: anything not matched → customer home ──
# (comment this out if you want a real 404 page)
# /*              /customer/index.html    200
